<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 06:09:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登：哈马斯被摧毁之前战争不会结束；联合国安理会呼吁“紧急”暂停加沙行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</link><description>以色列国防军公布两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字 ■ 拜登表示，重新占领加沙将是“一个大错误” ■ 联合国安理会呼吁“紧急”停火并无条件释放人质 ■ 以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩真主党 ■ 巴勒斯坦报告：以色列国防军重新进入希法，进行挖掘 ■ 以色列反对派领袖猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，提议由另一位利库德集团成员领导新政府 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀，239 名人质在加沙被扣 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</guid></item><item><title>警方在民主党总部逮捕要求加沙停火的示威者后，犹太抗议者与亲以色列议员发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</link><description>国会警察暴力驱散了在民主党国会竞选委员会外参加跨宗教守夜活动和反对以色列加沙战争的公民不服从活动的示威者，要求议员支持停火。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，对加沙希法医院的袭击向哈马斯发出了坚定的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-the-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-is-a-firm-message-for-hamas/0000018b-d4eb-d423-affb-f7eb5c7b0000</link><description>以色列冒着采取复杂策略的风险，增加了与哈马斯核心安全基础设施的接触。以色列国防军希望发出信号，尽管当前的突袭目标有限，但其部队没有害怕进入的地方，也没有哈马斯可以感到安全的地方</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-the-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-is-a-firm-message-for-hamas/0000018b-d4eb-d423-affb-f7eb5c7b0000</guid></item><item><title>西方警告以色列：加沙战争损害我们与阿拉伯世界的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/west-warns-israel-gaza-war-harming-our-relations-with-arab-world/0000018b-d4ed-dffa-adef-f6ed91ea0000</link><description>美国和欧洲外交官告诉《国土报》，他们支持以色列对 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击作出反应，这让阿拉伯和穆斯林世界付出了代价 — — 特别是在平民伤亡不断增加以及以色列在医院开展军事行动的情况下</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 03:59:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/west-warns-israel-gaza-war-harming-our-relations-with-arab-world/0000018b-d4ed-dffa-adef-f6ed91ea0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管批评越来越多，拜登坚称以色列战争不会结束，直到哈马斯被彻底摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-growing-criticism-biden-insists-israel-war-wont-end-until-hamas-fully-destroyed/0000018b-d5da-df9a-ab8b-dfda85780000</link><description>由于民主党和他自己的国家机器内部日益不满，拜登的行动期限比以色列总理更紧迫 — — 更不用说政府试图在不给予太多氧气的情况下承认一场舆论战了</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 02:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-growing-criticism-biden-insists-israel-war-wont-end-until-hamas-fully-destroyed/0000018b-d5da-df9a-ab8b-dfda85780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的下一个惊喜来自约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-next-surprise-is-coming-from-the-west-bank/0000018b-d4d9-df9a-ab8b-ded9c6030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 00:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-next-surprise-is-coming-from-the-west-bank/0000018b-d4d9-df9a-ab8b-ded9c6030000</guid></item><item><title>为什么自由派西方反对以色列？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-the-liberal-west-is-against-israel/0000018b-d4d9-d423-affb-f7fbc57f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 00:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-the-liberal-west-is-against-israel/0000018b-d4d9-d423-affb-f7fbc57f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队不是帮派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-16/ty-article/the-israeli-army-is-not-a-gang/0000018b-d4d9-dffa-adef-f6d9c5820000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 23:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-16/ty-article/the-israeli-army-is-not-a-gang/0000018b-d4d9-dffa-adef-f6d9c5820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对派领袖猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，提议由另一位利库德集团成员领导新政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-slams-netanyahu-proposes-new-govt-led-by-another-likud-member/0000018b-d4fc-dffa-adef-f6fc77570000</link><description>以色列反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，以色列不能允许自己“与我们根本不信任的总理”进行长期军事行动。利库德集团前部长：“我对内塔尼亚胡感到愤怒，它从内心灼伤我”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 22:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-slams-netanyahu-proposes-new-govt-led-by-another-likud-member/0000018b-d4fc-dffa-adef-f6fc77570000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，90％的犹太人认为在不久的将来会爆发与以色列阿拉伯人的家庭暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/90-of-jews-see-domestic-violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</link><description>协议中心进行的民意调查显示，犹太人和阿拉伯社区的相互不信任程度急剧上升。 “10 月 7 日的集体创伤将影响未来几年各群体之间的关系”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/90-of-jews-see-domestic-violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列和哈马斯在释放人质人数、战斗暂停持续时间方面存在分歧，谈判陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉国土报，哈马斯寻求释放约 50 名人质，其中主要是妇女和儿童，以换取释放巴勒斯坦女性和未成年囚犯。以色列要求大幅增加人质人数</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</guid></item><item><title>“甘茨离开政府的那一刻，内塔尼亚胡的沙漏就翻转了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</link><description>要求甘茨开始计划退出紧急政府的不仅仅是政治利益。甘茨的退出策略也符合国家利益</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 20:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女奋力打破全球对哈马斯性暴力的沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</link><description>与许多其他领域一样，当谈到 10 月 7 日揭露哈马斯基于性别的暴力时，以色列公民介入了政府留下的巨大空白</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 19:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</guid></item><item><title>新研究表明，大卫和所罗门的圣经王国可能确实存在</title><l