f3a70ff40000</link><description>无论是在古代还是近代历史中，中东和世界各地的城市都曾经被摧毁过。对于各国来说，这是一场地震事件。正如 10 月 7 日改变了一切一样，加沙城的毁灭也将改变一切</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 16:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-in-ruins-the-largest-palestinian-city-in-the-world-soon-uninhabitable/0000018b-d3a4-d423-affb-f3a70ff40000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔调解的加沙以色列人质释放谈判取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</link><description>据路透社周三报道，卡塔尔调解员正在寻求谈判一项协议，其中包括释放约 50 名人质，以换取为期三天的停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 15:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列渴望生命，就必须改变对巴勒斯坦人的态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</guid></item><item><title>“隐蔽的反犹太主义已变得完全公开”：以色列海外学生面临仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</link><description>自以色列-加沙战争爆发以来，外国医学院的以色列学生报告称，他们发现自己受到攻击</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</guid></item></channel></rss>